title: Ezekiel & Aconsumer - All We Have is Now
description:
The first installment of the All We Have is Now artist collaboration series takes us to South Africa with Aconsumer aka Lyall Coburn. Shot in 16mm and created with an original score.

From Aconsumer: 
"Often the most beautiful of moments are overlooked by us in our day to day lives. This film abstractly highlights one of life's simple pleasures, holding us in that moment, illustrating that in fact, All We Have Is Now."

asset.author: EZEKIELUSA
